issue.title: Install Gazebo .proto files so custom messages can use them

content.raw: Anonymous says: "Including .proto files in the installation package would allow Developers using non-supported Gazebo language platforms that are supported by Google protobuf language bindings to be compiled for sending messages to the Gazebo Simulator."
